/**
 * ModernNavigation (FIXED VERSION)
 * - FIXED: Popstate now properly updates all navigation URLs to match current language
 * - FIXED: Clear separation between dev mode (localhost) and production
 * - FIXED: Proper sync with languageManager on navigation
 */

